name: Tweedia
body:
### Welcome to Tweedia Site.

Tweedia is a GUI-base shell software specialized for analyzing results of called programs.

* Operaiton of Tweedia is validated on Mac OS X (Snow Leoperd).
* Tweedia is a free software distributed under GPL.

![screenshot](./images/screenshot.png)

Twitter: [@tweediaproj](https://twitter.com/tweediaproj)
